    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or as a donor for parts. The exterior shows significant neglect, with heavy rust bubbling on the quarter panels, rocker panels, and several deep scratches and dents across the body. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly, likely requiring a major tune-up or overhaul, and the suspension feels quite loose. The interior has significant wear, including torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold as-is, and we recommend a trailer for transport.",
